release_note: I made the settings perfect.
Maintaining the code base
Added support for Apple Silicon. Added privacy information.
Redesigned scale indicator. Added the ability to hide the scale indicator. Fixed theme color issue on iOS 14. Corrected the description for the Mac version.

Update 5.2.0 for iPad iPhone and Mac Dedicated to my father Wang Chenghae Today is June 18 2020 an auspicious number that is dad s favorite. Even though he had a brain hemorrhage he suddenly found himself in heaven.My father was an ordinary person with a very kind heart and even when he was under pressure he always kept a smile on his face. She supported my dreams my mother s dreams and our family with all her might. You love rock music and when you agreed to make a video to support your dreams you suddenly left. Dad it s too early to leave. I wanted to go see my girlfriend s grandmother. Maybe my turtle Raffles is waiting there too. The last time I was awake before you left I was worrying about my schoolwork. Don t worry Dad. With your support I really learned everything. Things I want to learn: development music theory Linguistics film history design psychology photography game design development translation writing economics leadership business etc. I m probably one of the few people who has watched classes from all departments at the university. And I have a clear vision of what I want to study in the future. The learning will come at WWDC in a few days so don t worry dad let s continue the fun lifelong learning already. This app is probably the most talked about app in the last few months Dad. Even though I don t have the equipment to use myself they always give me suggestions and ideas to help me get the right product for the user and they always help me when I need it. Even if I tell you not to rush don t get discouraged along with me but be patient and take your time to encourage me. Your support and love I really feel I also pass on your expectations and your support to all users. We would like to receive Dad s support and trust as well as your heart into this app and all future products and share them with the world! This update includes announcements translated into languages around the world for users around the world. Let people around the world know who you are on iPad iPhone and Mac. I have a wonderful father named Wang Chenge. I Wang Yuxi am very proud to be your son and will be your son again in the next life. I want everyone who reads this announcement to love those around him as much as he did in the last moments of his life. Remember to take care of your family s health and develop good habits. I miss you Dad. Take care. Mom and I love you.
